headline: 5 Revealing Analyst Questions From Travelers’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Travelers delivered results in line with Wall Street’s revenue expectations for Q4, as management credited strong underwriting performance and investment income for the company’s non-GAAP earnings beat.
